#
HEALTH_REGENERATION

This variable shows your character's current health regeneration per minute.
Powers such as regeneration and curing saturation affect your health
regeneration score.

See also: man power regeneration, man power curing saturation, man spec
regeneration

#
STAMINA_REGENERATION

This variable shows your character's current stamina regeneration per minute.

See also: help stamina

#
MOVEMENT_REGENERATION

This variable shows your character's current movement regeneration per minute.

#
WEATHER

This variable shows the weather for the current room your character is in.

See also: help weather

#
OPPONENT_HEALTH

This variable shows your currently engaged opponent's health percentage.

#
OPPONENT_NAME

This variable shows your currently engaged opponent's name.

#
OPPONENT_LEVEL

This variable shows your currently engaged opponent's level.

#
SPIRIT

This variable shows your current spirits available to your character.

See also: help spirit
